{"id":688282,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/688282.html","date":"2022-10-13T18:45:59Z","modified":"2022-10-16T09:31:17Z","title":"【404文库】不从｜那个时刻","content":"<div style=\"text-align:center;margin-top:26px;margin-bottom:26px\">\n\n<!-- iframe plugin v.4.5 wordpress.org/plugins/iframe/ -->\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://open.firstory.me/embed/story/cl98c3mp30m6a010k9fcpg8ii\" height=\"180\" width=\"700\" scrolling=\"yes\" class=\"iframe-class\" frameborder=\"0\"></iframe>\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"width:100%;margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\">\n<strong>标题：</strong>那个时刻<br />\n<strong>作者：</strong>不从<br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2022.10.13<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/r7SuJBn-bpjV4zliAZb0Gw\" target=\"_blank\">微信公众号“不从”</a><br>\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/四通桥横幅\" target=\"_blank\">四通桥横幅</a><br>\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">公民馆</a><br>\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p>这就是你生活的全部意义<br />\n从森林中选出一片最特别的树叶<br />\n作为一滴水落进平静的油锅<br />\n成为那个浓烟滚滚的时刻</p>\n<p>因为受够了夜晚就变成火炬<br />\n你举起了真正的自己<br />\n作为一个人落进荒诞的生活<br />\n成为那个一无所有的时刻</p>\n<p>这就是你消失的全部意义<br />\n从城墙中凿开一块最坚硬的砖<br />\n作为一盆凉水泼在火山内部<br />\n成为暴风雨的第一个音符</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2022/10/image-1665684903586.png\" alt=\"file\" /></p>\n","author":1089,"categories":[38917,45444,45870,41492,43134,45438],"tags":[9213,13222,14709,46081,46082,24294,46074,46065,46087]}